column5: Today me dad and one of his friends  went out fishing. I caught this, my very first,  king king king fish  this fish was a 39  inch  king salmon  it was a screamer.  It took me about 15 min to bring it in and when Dad got it in the net the handle bent.  this fish took us all  over the lake
G-man is kicking the kings,and adding inches to team One.  Nice fish little man.
Beauty fish G-man, way to go and some more inches for us
Awesome G. You are kicking button!!
You have a nag on catching big FISH   Way to go Young man
Congrats my little man. I will think long and hard before I say - "Fish On - ah , you can have that one Garreth" again. Nicely done son. That was  a beauty battle
Awesome!  Way to go big fella!
Way to go buddy. That's a beauty. Gotta love getting that king for the first.
Nice work, G!  Nothing like having a big chinook on the line, you've made a lot of people on this board very jealous!  :-)
39inches WOW there big already go get em G-man, show the old boys how its done
I am in awe G  Thats one beauty of a fish !! You da man !
rotten kid!!!! Nice shooting G...im going to buy your dad a very sharp knife to start cutting your line...  Nice report !
That's HUGE!!!! Your a great fisherman.
